src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Tim-Westwood-2@2000x1270.jpg" alt="蒂姆·韦斯特伍德" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Tim-Westwood-2@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Tim-Westwood-2@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Tim-Westwood-2@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Tim-Westwood-2@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Tim-Westwood-2@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Tim-Westwood-2@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3523942" class="wp-caption-text">蒂姆·韦斯特伍德。图片来源：Joseph Okpako/WireImage/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>现在，在周六（10月26日）发表的<a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c937yrezl7po" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BBC News</em></a>的一篇文章中，大都会警察发言人与<em>BBC新闻</em>分享了一份更新：“我们已经看到了该报告，并向<em>BBC</em>提出了有关该报告的各个部分可能会干扰正义的建议。如果出版。”</p><p>媒体补充说，该报告还将在下个月发布。</p><p>去年，据报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tim-westwood-interviewed-over-sexual-assault-allegations-3429240">韦斯特伍德（Westwood）在警方谨慎接受了</a>五项性犯罪指控，据说这是在1982年至2016年之间在伦敦发生的。</p><p>几个月后，一条<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-phone-line-opens-in-bbc-tim-westwood-sexual-misconduct-investigation-3433263">24小时的热线打开</a>，使人们可以匿名提供有关<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tim-westwood">蒂姆·韦斯特伍德</a>所谓的性行为不端的证据。据报道，据报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tim-westwood-sexual-misconduct-hotline-receives-important-information-3444335">热线索林收到了“大量重要的新信息</a>”，并在2023年10月确认DJ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tim-westwood-interviewed-fourth-time-by-police-amid-sexual-assault-allegations-3523936">第四次接受了大都会警察的采访</a>。</p><p><strong>有关帮助，建议或更多有关在英国性骚扰，攻击和强奸的信息，请访问<a href="http://rapecrisis.org.uk/index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">强奸危机慈善网站</a>。在美国，参观<a href="https://www.rainn.org/index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">雷恩</a>。</strong></p><p> 《邮报<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/met-police-warn-bbc-report-into-dj-tim-westwood-sexual-assault-allegations-may-interfere-with-justice-3807159">》会议警方警告BBC报告DJ Tim Westwood性侵犯指控“可能会干扰司法”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
